{
  "stem": "9503.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I know that my mother asked these questions to other survivors and-- because my father hadn't come back.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then, somehow or other, I think the message was given to me that my father wasn't going to come back, and I didn't believe that.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I remember sitting, especially when I still was in the regular-- in the grammar school, waiting for the door to open probably for a year.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it didn't, of course.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I thought he was maybe a prisoner in-- in Russia somewhere, you know, anything but.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] And apparently-- I-- I just looked in this-- this diary that I started in '47-- at that point, I had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] accepted the fact that my father wasn't going to come back, because I wrote it.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But in the beginning, I-- I just expected him to appear, you know, just a little later than the rest.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So otherwise, I-- I-- I can only say that I spent the first three years of-- of this-- the-- the lyceum life almost in a frivolous way.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I did my homework, but the emphasis was on-- on sports, on going to the dances, on-- on having a good time.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Did you write anything besides your diaries after the war?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Did you keep any records of things that had happened?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wrote down, at one point, and I don't remember where, all the songs and poems and-- and all those [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] things that I remembered about the camp.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were songs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In Westerbork, actually, I was in a-- in a choir that sang for the commandant, including one Hebrew song.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I still don't-- I can't forget that one.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
